    <exercise xml:id="x2_1_11">
      <statement>
        <p>
          Suppose <m>f</m> is a one-to-one mapping from <m>D</m> onto <m>T</m> and that <m>A</m> is a subset of <m>D</m>.
        </p>
        <task>
